<br>
Launch date of LOY.  Exploring Crypt of Nadox with group, find the boss mob, Spiritseeker Nadox.  Boss is in a large room with 8 other spawns.  My group sets up in the hall before the room and pull the 2 mobs at entrance to the room and kill.  Continue to pull mobs from boss room, clear the 4 spawns at back of room and then move INTO the room.<br>
<br>
We are now looking at 2 mobs in front of named, 2 mobs behind him on wall.  We pull and clear 2 in front of named.  Left with named, and 2 on wall.<br>
<br>
Summary, group cleared way to room, group cleared entrance mobs, moved INTO room and continued clearing.<br>
<br>
Now we pull one of the far mobs behind named because didn't want them to add when we pulled named.  Fighting mob, member of another group runs in and pulls named out to hallway !!!<br>
<br>
We are like WTF ??? We cleared the whole damn room, moved INTO it, next pull would've been named, and these assholes just run right in and pull the named out ??? Now heres the even more @#%$ up part.  Their group was using 2 charmed and hasted pets, of which both charms broke on pull of named, thus that group got wasted.  My group was VERY capable of taking the named, but because these assholes pulled the name out from us, then lost their charmed pets and died, we now had 1 named full HP, and 2 charmed and hasted 200 hitting mobs aggro on us and kill us all...<br>
<br>
We died as well of course with no crowd control.  Is that the most screwed up thing you ever heard ? I mean sure its launch day, everyone is excited and once to kill new mobs etc.  But sheesh come on, blatantly running into a cleared room while a group is fighting in it and pulling the named out is just flat out WRONG.  I don't care if it's launch day, thats BS and total crap.<br>
<br>
THen after getting rezzes we are obviously /ooc ing about what happened, people are backing us up saying they saw us in the room and clearing it, and these fuckheads in the group that pulled the named start spouting off &quot;you cleared the room, so what? grats to you, want a cookie ?&quot;  I mean wtf ? Then they start making up @#%$ saying &quot;there are 3 rooms with the named you cleared the one not all of them&quot;. Ok well first off how can a named be in 3 rooms ? Second, there is ONE room one large room with 8 spawns and 2 hallways on opposite sides leading in to it, we cleared from the hallway INTO the room and cleared the room.  These assholes just ran in from the hallway and pulled named, so where the hell is this 3 room @#%$ coming from ???<br>
<br>
Sorry for the vent  but this is the rants forum afterall ! So in conclusion I had every right to be pissed off right ? I wrote down three of the names I caught and their guilds and vow never to group with them ever.  I told a few friends about it and they all laughed and said &quot;yeah their guild is known for that type of @#%$&quot;.  So anyway I'm pissed lol <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
